column4: I am trying to installing tor project according to this tutorial: http://www.torproject.org/docs/debian.html.en#ubuntu . I have inserted: http://deb.torproject.org/torproject.org lucid main   in /etc/apt/sources.list and saved it. i ran gpg --keyserver keys.gnupg.net --recv 886DDD89  and then gpg --export A3C4F0F979CAA22CDBA8F512EE8CBC9E886DDD89 | sudo apt-key add -   as described. when i then however run sudo apt-get update i get the foll
owing: E: Type 'http://deb.torproject.org/torproject.org' is not known on line 59 in source list /etc/apt/sources.list  What am i doing wrong?
